What's on the honey-do list
today from good old richard?

00:10.370 --> 00:11.470
You know what?

00:11.470 --> 00:12.910
Shut up with your honey-do
because...

00:12.910 --> 00:14.380
[ phone rings ]
oh, that's -- oh.

