<i> Have y'all eaten?</i>
No.

00:21.480 --> 00:23.120
<i> Y'all want to come get</i>
<i> some tacos?</i>

00:23.120 --> 00:25.290
I like tacos. Cool.
We're on our way.

00:25.290 --> 00:27.620
<i> Bye.</i>
<i> See y'all in a minute.</i>

00:27.620 --> 00:30.790
Tacos, this day
just gets better and better.

00:30.790 --> 00:32.460
All right.
Boy, my boy tony has got you.

00:32.460 --> 00:34.930
-That's overconfidence.
-No, I've seen tony eat.

